### 6. query_builder.py (facade) (~150-200 lines)
**Purpose:** Facade coordinating all sub-services

```python
class QueryBuilder:
    """
    Unified query builder facade.

    Delegates to specialized sub-services:
    - QueryOptimizer: Index-aware optimization
    - QueryTemplateManager: Template management
    - QueryValidator: Validation and syntax checking
    - FacetedQueryBuilder: Faceted search
    - GraphContextBuilder: Graph traversal
    """

    def __init__(self, schema_service):
        self.schema_service = schema_service
        self.logger = get_logger("UnifiedQueryBuilder")

        # Initialize all sub-services
        self.optimizer = QueryOptimizer(schema_service)
        self.templates = QueryTemplateManager(schema_service)
        self.validator = QueryValidator(schema_service)
        self.faceted = FacetedQueryBuilder(schema_service)
        self.graph = GraphContextBuilder(schema_service)

    # Delegation methods (one line each)
    async def build_optimized_query(self, request):
        return await self.optimizer.build_optimized_query(request)

    def register_template(self, name, spec, category="custom"):
        return self.templates.register_template(name, spec, category)

    async def from_template(self, template_name, **params):
        return await self.templates.from_template(template_name, **params)

    # ... (25 more delegation methods)
